Description: We provide the Microsoft Academic Knowledge Graph (MAKG)- a large RDF data set with over eight billion triples with information about scientific publications and related entities- such as authors- institutions- journals- and fields of study. The data set is based on the Microsoft Academic Graph and licensed under the Open Data Attributions license. Furthermore- we provide entity embeddings for all 210M represented scientific papers.
